      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">You cause a 30-foot-diameter sphere of water or other liquid to fill with bioluminescent plankton, increasing the light level from dark to dim or from dim to normal. For the spell&rsquo;s duration, you can take a standard action to move this area up to 30 feet in any direction. You can also take a standard action to condense the plankton into a tight, brightly glowing ball at the center of the sphere. If you do so, each creature that starts its turn in or enters the spell&rsquo;s area must attempt a Will save or become fascinated until the beginning of its next turn. A creature that saves against this effect is immune to it for 24 hours. This spell has no effect above water.</span></p>"
